Name: Jessica Secret of the Caribbean
About the game: Jessica Secret of the Caribbean is a classic hidden object game with a gripping storyline and a lot of mini-games. Jessica and Tony fall in love, get married and go for a sweet honeymoon to the Caribbean. Things don't go according to plan when they get involved in a whole new hidden object adventure! Help Jessica rescue her kidnapped husband by finding the riches of Jessica's forefather, the famous pirate, Noel! - Incredible atmosphere - Fantastic gameplay - Rescue Jessica's husband!
